      <li><strong>Practice</strong>: Each section includes practical examples and common interview questions.</li>
      <li><strong>Review</strong>: Use our checklists and summaries to reinforce your learning.</li>
    </ol>
    
    <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900 rounded-lg">
